HR NO. 405 ENROLLED
WHEREAS, New Orleans-based Consul General of the French Republic, the
Honorable Rodolphe Sambou, is a passionate fan of Les Rouge-et-Bleu; and
WHEREAS, Paris Saint-Germain Football Club is most deserving of the highest
recognition for winning European soccer's most-prestigious prize: the UEFA Champions
League Trophy.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Paris Saint-Germain Football Club on
winning its second consecutive UEFA Champions League title and does hereby extend
sincerest wishes that club continue to prosper in all of its competitive endeavors for many
more years to come.
